message.content: Wang Xijie's father-in-law is the Wanli Emperor.
The director of "The Boss and the Worker" died first.
Maximilian Karl, 6th Prince of Thurn and Taxis died in 1871.
The director of "Mille chilometri al minuto!" died later.
Sir Thomas Lawley, 3rd Baronet's paternal grandfather is Sir Thomas Lawley, 1st Baronet.
The director of "An Italian Romance" died later.
Countess Palatine Anna Magdalena of Birkenfeld-Bischweiler was born in Bischweiler.
Princess Florestine's paternal grandmother is Maria Caroline Gibert de Lametz.
Les Mayfield was born in Albuquerque, New Mexico.
Henri I, Duke of Nemours' paternal grandfather was Henri de Savoie.
